About this item

  • NOURISH & STRENGTHEN: Our nutrient-rich, biotin-infused treatment can be used as part of your everyday hair care routine or as an intensive deep treatment to prevent damage for strong, lustrous hair with a fresh, invigorating scent
  • SMOOTH SPLIT ENDS: This lightweight treatment nourishes split ends and hair follicles for a sleek look; Apply to the ends of hair before you shampoo to soothe and smooth for a healthy, shiny finish that can be air-dried or styled as desired
  • SOOTHE DRY SCALP: This rich blend of over 30 essential oils and nutrients deeply penetrates the scalp to increase circulation, combat dandruff, and comfort itchy, sensitive skin while working to strengthen, lengthen, nourish, and protect hair
  • SAFE FOR ALL HAIR TYPES: Our versatile Rosemary Mint Scalp & Hair Strengthening Oil promotes radiant hair for all hair types and deeply nourishes types 3A to 4C, chemically-treated hair, braids, weaves, and both low and high porosity level hair
  • BY WOMEN FOR WOMEN: Mielle Organics aims to empower women of all hair types and styles with powerful products and gentle, organic ingredients that amplify your natural beauty and are the root to results that leave you looking and feeling your best

Product Description

Faster and thicker hair

Both rosemary and mint essential oils are known to increase blood circulation which allows for more oxygen to be carried to your scalp. More oxygen will stimulate your hair follicles, resulting in faster and thicker hair.

Longer and Heathier

If increasing your hair length is one of your top hair concerns, then you have come to the right place. For the women wearing their hair in protective styles, just a couple drops of our Rosemary Mint Strengthening Oil at your roots is what you need to keep your strands long and luscious.

Shinier Hair

For a bouncy, natural style, use our Rosemary Mint Strengthening Shampoo and bring back shine to your curly hair! With a combination of our natural ingredients and commitment to a strict hair regime, your definition of healthy hair will be taken to a whole new level.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Nurul Muneim
4.0 out of 5 stars Quality
Reviewed in the United States on June 15, 2023
Verified Purchase
I recently tried the Mielle Organics Rosemary Mint Scalp & Hair Strengthening Oil, and I'm happy to give it a four-star review. This nourishing treatment is packed with beneficial ingredients that promote scalp health and strengthen hair. Here's why I think it's worth considering:

Effective Scalp Nourishment: The Rosemary Mint Scalp & Hair Strengthening Oil provides excellent nourishment for the scalp. The combination of rosemary, mint, and essential oils creates a refreshing and invigorating experience while helping to improve the overall condition of the scalp. It soothes dryness and itchiness, contributing to a healthier scalp environment.

Strengthening Properties: This oil contains biotin and essential oils known for their hair-strengthening benefits. Biotin helps promote healthy hair growth and reduces the likelihood of breakage, while the essential oils contribute to improving hair strength and resilience. With regular use, I noticed a decrease in the appearance of split ends and a general improvement in the overall condition of my hair.

Versatility for All Hair Types: The Mielle Organics Rosemary Mint Scalp & Hair Strengthening Oil is suitable for all hair types. Whether you have straight, wavy, curly, or coily hair, this treatment can be incorporated into your hair care routine. It helps provide moisture, nourishment, and overall scalp health regardless of your specific hair texture.

Pleasant Aroma: The rosemary mint scent of this oil is refreshing and invigorating. It leaves a subtle fragrance in the hair that lasts throughout the day. The aroma is not overpowering, making it suitable for those who prefer a more subtle scent in their hair care products.

While I highly appreciate the Mielle Organics Rosemary Mint Scalp & Hair Strengthening Oil, there are a few points that prevented me from giving it a full five-star rating:

Size and Price: The 2-fluid ounce size of this oil may be limiting for those who require a larger amount or plan to use it frequently. Additionally, the price point can be a bit higher compared to other hair oils on the market. Considering the quantity and cost, some may find it more suitable as a targeted treatment rather than an everyday product.
